spub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula> (<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/13-2390136x62_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>)都很小，那么<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/13-2390136x63_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>与<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/13-2390136x64_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>之间的线性关系就不明显。所以可令原假设为</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.16113-formula264"><graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/13-2390136x65_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>当<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/13-2390136x66_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>成立时，</p><disp-formula id="hanspub.16113-formula265"><label>(10)</label><graphic position="anchor" xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/13-2390136x67_hanspub.png"  xlink:type="simple"/></disp-formula><p>其中，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/13-2390136x68_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/13-2390136x69_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>是总离差平方和，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/13-2390136x70_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>是残差平方和，<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/13-2390136x71_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>是回归平方和。在显著性水平<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/13-2390136x72_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>下有上<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/13-2390136x73_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-formula>分为点<inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="http://html.hanspub.org/file/13-2390136x74_hanspub.png" xlink:type="simple"/></inline-fo